name: Genius Club
summary:
Synopsis

From the moment I was born, Ive had the same dream every day, where the same day repeats itself endlessly.
What did you do in your dream?
Robbed banks, blew up buildings, flirted with girls, joyrode in luxury cars Since it was a dream, naturally, I did a lot of lawless things.
Tell me about your dream last night.
Yesterday was quite interesting. After dreaming for so long, it was the first time I dreamed about someone I know in real life. She was a very beautiful girl
Mhm.
The police officer Uncle nodded as he took notes:
Keep going, Im listening.
